data.description: This property would be an ideal choice for both first-time homebuyers and savvy investors. With 4 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms across its spacious 2,016 square feet, this home offers ample space for comfortable living. Situated on a nearly one-quarter acre corner lot, it features expansive front and back yards, perfect for outdoor activities and gardening. Two wood burning fireplaces give a cozy ambiance and are an added option for heating. One of the standout features of this property is its enviable location, directly across the street from Sportsman's Park in Post Falls. Whether you're looking for a place to call your own or an investment opportunity, this property offers the best of both worlds. Its versatile layout, sizable lot, and prime location make it an obvious choice. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home or add it to your investment portfolio. It's a fantastic find in a great location.
